Customer Service Manager
Emenac
-
Lahore
Emenac Inc. offers a strong career opportunity for Self Motivated & Energetic Female staff.
We are looking for Professional & only Experienced Customer Service Manager for our American Inbound call center. She should have an excellent command over English Language as she has to communicate with clients abroad. She must be computer literate.
Emenac Inc. offers a strong career opportunity for Self Motivated & Energetic Female staff.
We are looking for Professional & only Experienced Customer Service Manager for our American Inbound call center. She should have an excellent command over English Language as she has to communicate with clients abroad. She must be computer literate.
Skills Required:
The selected candidate must be target-oriented and highly motivated and must have flair for achieving challenging goals.
Must be able to handle escalation
Must be available for work during Night Shift (9.00pm - 5.00am)
Must be a hardworking/disciplined individual.
Must be outgoing an extrovert
Must have excellent capability of learning and serving.
Must be fluent in English, desirous to learn and excel professionally
Must have international English accent.
Must be a team player.
Must be punctual
Note: We are looking for individuals Girls who can work in the night shift from 9.00pm till 5.00am.
